    Walk softly, and carry a black stick.
~

-1 PK~
The Way of the PKer in the Realm of `&A``n`&i``m`&e M``U`&D``...

Here in the realm of Anime, you have the ability and choice to Player Kill,
also known as PK. To become a player killer you must type "pk" <enter> "pk"
<enter again>. By doing this you have therefore stated that you have chosen
the path of the "Player Killer" and accept full responsibility for knowing
the rules of "Player Killing".

See Also: Help (PK_RULES, PK_RULES2, MULTIKILLING, GROUP_KILLING, DEAD, OOL)
~

-1 PK_RULES~
The PK-Rules in the Realm of `&A``n`&i``m`&e M``U`&D``...

1. You must be within the `!7`` Levels of your Oppenent. 

2. Your target MUST be PK set, it is illegal to, in some way or other 
   fashion, bring aggressive mobs to any NON-PK person in the game. 
   It is also illegal to bring the character to the mob, via summon or other
   way, to an aggressive mob.

3. It is legal to PK a person with ANY charmed mob as long as you 
   yourself have chosen the path of the player killer. 

4. Charmed Mobs and Aggressive Mobs can be manipulated in any fashion to 
   gain a successful "PK". Although, it IS illegal to summon aggressives 
   into town. It IS illegal to order your PC charmy to attack a sure kill
   mobile. (In time this will be hard-coded) Take note of the last lines
   of '`@HELP CHARM``' also for PK reference.

5. Please do not flood the channels about your loss in a PK battle. If 
   you gathered all your eq. Then im sure you can gather more again. Even 
   though losing in PK battle is terrible, least you can take revenge later.

6. If a character you come across is LINK-DEAD, assume they are and 
   leave them alone to their linkdead self. 

Continued with: help 'PK_RULES2'
~

-1 PK_RULES2~
7.  It is illegal for Non-Pkers to interfere with any PKset persons 
    kills. Whether you are trying to keep the eq from the person who
    PKed him. If you are NONPK then simply have no relation in PK
    events. If you decide you wish to help out a PKer and are NONPK
    then you yourself the NONPK will become PKset.

8.  It is legal for a person to be killed while they are AFK. Although
    this is a cheap thing to be done. You should learn to camp out at
    the healer or a safe room whenever you need to go AFK. If there is
    a real emergency in real life that calls for you to be AFK 'that 
    second' then there will be no reason for you to get upset that you
    lost your corpse.

9.  People with Killer flags shall keep their flags until they have
    either served a period of time, up to immortal, or have the consent
    to remove the flag from the person of which they PKed. This goes
    along with the Thief flag also.

10. If you didn't kill em, don't loot em. Leave the corpse alone even
    if you are pkset. It wasn't your kill to begin with. Tampering
    with corpses you didn't kill for will result in punishment.

*** These are not finalized Rules. More may be added if necessary. ***
~

-1 MULTI MULTIKILLING~
Multikilling in the Realm of `&A``n`&i``m`&e M``U`&D``...

Multikilling, like on most other muds, is when you kill the same person
over and over again with you starting and finishing the initial attack.
This is extremely illegal, and can result in loss of level/hp/mana/move or
deletion. Time until you can kill an oppenent again is 24 hours System/Rl
time. Multikilling also involves the use of dragging an oppenent to an
aggro mobile or aggro to them. If he/she's died by your hands already
leave them alone till tomorrow!
~

-1 GROUP_KILLING~
Group Killing in the Realm of `&A``n`&i``m`&e M``U`&D`  `...

When grouped, the higher level character on will be responsible for the 
actions of the rest of his group. During PK battles, the highest level 
will be held accountable whether or not they are within or out of level.
~

-1 OOL~
OOL in the Realm of `&A``n`&i``m`&e M``U`&D``...

OOL, or Out of Level, is also very illegal here. Keep in mind that the pk
range of this MUD is 7 levels. Anyone that is killed or attacked out of 
that level range is considered OOL. If you are a true pker and worthy 
enough, then you wouldn't have to pick on someone younger than yourself.
~

